ottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">最近，吃面好像比较有风险。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">榆林一位可怜的司机，只是想吃碗炒面，不想就遭到了面馆里一位“制服男”的羞辱和殴打，一边打还一边嚷：“你没看我穿的制服吗”？</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">我早已经厌恶了写这些破事，但是奈何这些破事总是发生。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">别的都不多说了，只想讲一点：对这件事，很多人虽然感觉愤怒和离谱，却可能因为听不懂方言，没有完全看懂完整的过程。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">恰好我有个朋友，能听懂视频里的方言，就帮我翻译了一下，结果信息量大增。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">整件事最戏剧性、也最讽刺的，还不是什么制服男恃强凌弱，狗仗皮势，而是一个很有趣的细节：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;">制服大爷其实并不是突然发火、突然嚣张的，而是经过了一个小心翼翼、再三再四确认对方司机身份的过程。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;visibility: visible;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3386674554873577481" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FEC7unEiaL8xqtqgczq2UH5UtTAHZ9MrwUUaHV00PSPJVLf32R8nFgAZ0aug2BVJTMb8iaObfAkpEicRdk3wkC6qzw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7935222672064777" data-w="886" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3386674554873577481"></iframe></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -app