        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDEzNTMyMA==&amp;mid=2650328916&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c2b090324754ab7641b8c1210ab2bdf4&amp;chksm=87e7b3a3b0903ab52b9f9f29ad4760568e2ca7467d00ab5ad3d07981ba911a63dc36c6a3c417#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-03-25T13:00:20.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845263" data-ratio="0.7657407407407407" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xpHEEgzBVCjl57fV4AhFLGiahy1C7cNAqVqLzb3vpEqhU1G1zHib1dRTjUs0gvZHeReAF4libEhvXNqg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">文/六神磊磊</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">一<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></strong><strong style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">杨康其实很像一个人——</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">乔峰</span><span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">。</span><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 16px;"><br><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">说到这里，你可能就要不服了：杨康也配？配不配先不论，发现没，少年杨康一开始和乔峰的命运很像，甚至说他俩是另一个时空的对方都行，剧本大差不差。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">他们都自幼家破亲亡，流落异国，被仇家养大。偏偏仇家对他们都不错，又给身份，又给资源，尽心尽力培育成人。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">少年的他们，出道即巅峰，辽人乔峰在大宋当了帮主，人人钦仰，宋人杨康在大金做小王爷，众星捧月。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">乔峰自以为是宋人，一直以对抗辽国为己任，杨康自以为是金人，时刻以屠灭大宋为目标。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">偏偏命运开了一样的玩笑，他们都被旁人揭穿，你不叫乔峰，叫萧峰，他不叫完颜康，叫杨康，那一刻，人生的齿轮开始吱嘎乱转。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">但转动的结果却天差地别，乔峰自不必多说，无论他姓乔还是姓萧，你觉得都一样，好汉，英雄，可“完颜康”听起来就活像骂人，成了小人、卑鄙的代名词。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">明明拿到手是乔峰的剧本，怎么就活成了完颜康？</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">二</strong></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 16px;">杨康的人生太依赖好剧本，像打牌一样，只会打好牌，还把命运的馈赠误以为是自己的能力。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">出场的时候，少年杨康约莫十七八岁年纪，容貌英俊，身份尊贵，武艺高强，陌上人如玉，公子世无双，标准的偶像男主剧本。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">这个时候的杨康最自信，也最舒展，如果不出意外的话，就会像干爹完颜洪烈给他规划的：<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>他日我大权在手<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">……</span>这锦绣江山，花花世界，日后尽都是你的了。<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">那一刻，少年热血沸腾，梦里的阳光都是七彩的：<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>大事若成，我岂不成了天下共主？<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">可人生总是充满了意外，剧本说换就换，乔峰这边，丐帮帮主别当了，你材料出问题了，滚回你的契丹去；那边，杨康你其实是农家子弟，牛家村的老房还在，收拾收拾回去住罢。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">也就是从这里开始，二人选择不同，命运也走向了截然不同的反面。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">乔峰道：<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>阿朱，我是契丹人，从今而后，不再以契丹人为耻，也不以大宋为荣。<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span>他坦然接受了自己是契丹人的现实。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">而杨康呢，不仅不接受现实，反而是愤怒地挺枪刺向农夫爸爸杨铁心的咽喉：</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span><span style="font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">难道我要舍却荣华富贵，跟这穷汉子浪迹江湖，不，万万不能。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845259" data-ratio="0.7361111111111112" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xpHEEgzBVCjl57fV4AhFLGiaH5OibV6M9I25L1ndZax0AaAI3v4iaIMdGteg1yxq46qnM0piaOGnDlORQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;"></span></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">一句万万不能，表面是贪图荣华，潜台词其实就是牛家村的剧本我不会啊。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">三<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></strong><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">不会怎么办，强行换剧本。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">其实一开始，无论是武功还是智商，杨康在少年辈里还算出众的。对穆念慈是轻薄了点，但也谈不上罪大恶极，起码比动不动就要掳掠少女双修的梁子翁、欧阳克强一点。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">可由于对<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>小王爷<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span>的执念，杨康不择手段的要换回原来的剧本，拼命去讨好完颜洪烈，拼命想上位，以至于动作变形，道义也不要了，智商也掉线了。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">给完颜洪烈当先锋去盗武穆遗书，你盗书就盗书吧，非要捅郭靖一刀，本来郭靖对杨康多上心的，一定要弄成生死仇敌。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">急功近利之下，杨康的智商也逐渐不在线。他想拜师西毒欧阳锋，欧阳锋并未完全推拒，只说拜师不行，指点几招倒是可以。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">这其实是莫大福缘。试想北丐洪七公传艺于郭靖，一开始不也没让拜师，也是从指点几招开始的吗？</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">可杨康却毫无耐心，容不得半点折扣，立刻不高兴写了满脸，让欧阳锋当场下头。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">后来他更是干出害死欧阳克欲取而代之这样的昏招，彻底断了自己的生路。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">四<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></strong><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">反观乔峰，高下立判。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">乔峰的人生不靠剧本，也不稀罕剧本，<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>丐帮帮主<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span>不让做了是吧，那就不做了：<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>这帮主一职，是决计不再当了<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span>。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">不仅是开始时不做，后来丐帮众人求着他也不做：<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>多承各位重义，在下感激不尽，帮主之位，却是万万不能当的。<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">人，只有离开了平台，才能看明白：到底是平台的能力，还是你的能力？到底是剧本的馈赠，还是你自己的力量？</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">离开赵王府，杨康啥也不是，而乔峰离开丐帮还是乔峰，到了契丹，是威名赫赫的南院大王；去了女真部落，是响当当的打虎好汉。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">他还越活越精彩了，万军之中擒辽国皇太叔，平了大军叛乱；驱燕云十八飞骑闯中原，救阿紫，独斗当世三大高手。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">不但不在乎剧本，甚至他还可以直接推翻设定。当他把慕容复像抓小鸡一样提在手里，说萧某大好男儿如何和你齐名的时候，就是对天下宣布：</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">什么<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">“</span>北乔峰、南慕容<span style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;">”</span>？这个糟心设定从此作罢，萧某宣布立即维护更新。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">剧本咋写的我不管，自己的人生信条自己写，自己的人生自己说了算，所以乔峰过得豪气干云，气震山河，走到哪都是响当当的好汉。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;">五</strong></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">话说，命运这个东西，为什么残酷又有魅力，其实就在于老天只写了前一半，后一半仍然要自己写。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">人生如戏，没有哪个模版是注定最好的。杨康不择手段地换回小王爷的剧本，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">最后怎样？</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">剧本又变了，蒙古崛起了，“大金国的中都也给蒙古人攻下了，亡国之祸就是眼前的事”。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">就算没死在铁枪庙，杨康的人生也会再次被甩飞。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">古往今来活得最潇洒的，无过于苏东坡。他有一句话：“所可知者，常行于所当行，常止于不可不止。”</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">行所当行，是最大的痛快。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">有些聪明同学可能已经等不及了：</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">杨康+穆念慈+命运重启，你就直接说了吧是不是<strong><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">网易《射雕</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">》。</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845266" data-ratio="0.4546296296296296" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xpHEEgzBVCjl57fV4AhFLGiarLwb7zGUs8Y9tAncOUkib2FWxibAyTZdBIR1XwFC4aiaJRoI06H8dhK5Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">都看新闻了，28号全平台公测对不对？给我一个入坑的理由！难不成还能把杨康玩出乔峰的剧本？</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-