x;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845267" data-ratio="0.4935185185185185" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xpHEEgzBVCjl57fV4AhFLGiakqzqclOutrwBHuEicC9PwtYSdD6icFGiaKaBFBe3hnFcicAscluGmV6lpQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">之所以玩游戏，就是要一种重生穿越的感觉，让人物去活出新的生命，弥补之前的遗憾。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">而网易《射雕》一大好玩之处，就是多分支剧情，玩家自主演绎，还能回溯。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">除开郭靖黄蓉线，好比你选了杨康线，每一步都惊心动魄，随时面临选择，当然一切的挑战都是值得的，你的杨康可能玩出和原著截然不同的结局，变成萧峰郭靖一样顶天立地的英雄人物。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">我听说内测时不少玩家甚至玩出了杨铁心和包惜弱归隐山林的结局，真是让许多心系牛家村的原著粉内心一热。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">另外，网易《射雕》确实制</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">作精良，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">公布的郭靖杨康剧情</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">PV</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">《逆子》，这画面情节</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">，都是用以后日子不过了的方式去投入制作的。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">看这一段动画标准的打斗剧情：</span></p><p class="channels_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-videosnap class="js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe" data-pluginname="mpvideosnap" data-url="https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7Ym3K77SEULgkiat8kOQc4NchbDDhWH3aQHGu0icnD3z70MDUU1AYaiaianJBgQHm54mC2CGk6NwEA9fJ2eIhmY6L9M1D6QVq9Z