gb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">而网易的《射雕》是过关的，不能说每一个人物、场景都符合我的想象，该吐槽的我也吐了，但对原著的认真和尊重程度还是要肯定的。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="502845256" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xpHEEgzBVCjl57fV4AhFLGia8441ofmicfMg2icqXHZ2soUwPpwLhGIaEO2D4DfWnlQWbpQvrw7J1ehg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">而且《射雕》的惊喜不止于此，还有世界一服、拒绝PVP排名氪金、发起外观价格战等创举。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-feature-settings: normal;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-variation-settings: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">游戏将于3月28日上线，今天正式开放预下载，大家可以点击“阅读原文”去体验，还有好礼相送哦。</span></p><p style="font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-var